@startuml sequence-scoring-aggregate
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam defaultFontSize 13
skinparam dpi 150
skinparam sequenceParticipantBackgroundColor #F0EEF8
skinparam sequenceParticipantBorderColor #3D108A
skinparam sequenceActorBorderColor #3D108A
skinparam sequenceArrowColor #2E2E38
skinparam sequenceArrowFontSize 12
skinparam noteBorderColor #27ACAA
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #E8F8F8
skinparam noteFontSize 12

actor "Analyst" as U
participant "Results\nscreen" as R
participant "Scoring engine\n(application store)" as S

U -> R: open the Results screen
R -> S: request the maturity results
activate S
S -> S: compute each effective score
note right of S
  null if skipped or unanswered;
  capped at 2 if the score is 3 or
  more without evidence.
end note
S -> S: average within each sub-dimension
S -> S: average within each dimension
S -> S: weighted, renormalized Global Maturity Index
note right of S: GMI 2.19 gives 44 percent, Level 2 Emerging
S --> R: global score, dimension scores,\npercentage, maturity level
deactivate S
R -> R: render the radar chart, the dimension bars,\nand the maturity badge
@enduml
